## Network Security

- **WiFi credentials** are stored in `secrets.h` which is excluded from source control
- **OTA password** can optionally be set in `secrets.h` — required to upload firmware via ElegantOTA
- The web interface is only active when in WiFi-only or OTA mode; in normal operation WiFi is OFF
- Only devices on your local network can access the web interface
- Use WPA2 or WPA3 encryption on your WiFi network

