## Specifications

**Distance Sensor (VL53L1X):**
- Range: 40mm to 4000mm
- Field of View: 27°
- Accuracy: ±5% (±200mm at 4 meters) at best
- Timing budget: 200ms (configurable; valid values: 15, 20, 33, 50, 100, 200, 500 ms)
- Measurement interval: 1000ms (configurable), sketch reads every 10s

**Connectivity:**
- WiFi: 2.4GHz 802.11 b/g/n (active only in WiFi-only and OTA modes)
- Zigbee: End Device mode
- Web server: Port 80 (active only in WiFi-only and OTA modes)

**OTA Updates:**
- Maximum OTA/WiFi-only session: 15 minutes
- Auto-timeout returns to Zigbee mode
- ElegantOTA library (optional password protection)

**Power:**
- USB-C powered
- Typical consumption: ~100–200mA

